Title: Object: Sakieh près Esneh (Haute-Egypte)
Series: Les Artistes Contemporains
Description: A river landscape; a mother and child standing at the river's edge at left; beyond above a cliff, a cluster of trees at left and an ox-driven water pump at centre; in the far distance at right, a tower and a building with a dome; published in 'Les Artistes contemporains', seventh year of publication, 1852. Lithograph
Producer name: Print made by: Jean Joseph François Bellel
Curator's comments: From 'Les Artistes Contemporains', see 1889,0608.477 for comment on series
Bibliographic references: IFF / Inventaire du Fonds Français: Bibliothèque Nationale, Département des Estampes (5)
